Use the standard library
This is how to sum_product of numbers:
  Remember that total is 0
  Remember that prod is 1
  Do this numbers's length times:
    Remember that i is diff of numbers's length and numbers's length
    Increase i by 1
    Remember that i is diff of i and 1
    Remember that value is item i in numbers
    Remember that total is sum of total and value
    Remember that prod is product of prod and value
  End do
  The answer is [total, prod]
